Class ContactInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.trinkettrader.User.Profile.ContactInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observable

    public class ContactInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements Observable
    Class that serves as a container for contact information. This should appear as an attribute of a user. Whenever this class is used it should have been obtained by the getter contained in the user.

        public void notifyObservers()
        If hasChanged() returns true, calls the update() method for every observer in the list of observers using null as the argument. Afterwards, calls clearChanged().

        Equivalent to calling notifyObservers(null).
